{
  "page": "Aemon Rivers",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Rivers\" title=\"Aemon Rivers\"><img alt=\"Aemon Rivers.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/85/Aemon_Rivers.svg/50px-Aemon_Rivers.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/85/Aemon_Rivers.svg/75px-Aemon_Rivers.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/85/Aemon_Rivers.svg/100px-Aemon_Rivers.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Aemon Rivers</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Rivers\" title=\"Aemon Rivers\"><img alt=\"Aemon Rivers.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/85/Aemon_Rivers.svg/50px-Aemon_Rivers.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/85/Aemon_Rivers.svg/75px-Aemon_Rivers.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/85/Aemon_Rivers.svg/100px-Aemon_Rivers.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Aemon Rivers and Walda Rivers by coldraindropsss.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/ca/Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/300px-Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ca/Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/450px-Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ca/Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/600px-Aemon_Rivers_and_Walda_Rivers_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Aemon Rivers and his daughter Walda Rivers by coldraindropsss</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Rivers\" title=\"Walder Rivers\">Walder Rivers</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/House_Charlton\" title=\"House Charlton\">Charlton</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Rivers_(daughter_of_Aemon)\" title=\"Walda Rivers (daughter of Aemon)\">Walda Rivers</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Personal arms</span></th><td>\nQuarterly: a silver-grey castle on blue beneath a red bend sinister, three green mistletoes on gold bordered in green<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-sigil_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sigil-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><br />(<i>Quarterly clockwise, 1st and 3rd azure, a bridge cendrée, at either end a tower of the same, all debruised by a bend sinister gules, 2nd and 4th or, three mistletoes within a bordure vert</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Aemon Rivers</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> and the only son of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Rivers\" title=\"Walder Rivers\">Walder Rivers</a>, the oldest of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> sons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aemon_Rivers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to his grandfather, Lord Walder, Aemon never has anything sensible to say.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Like his father, Aemon also has a personal blazon.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sigil_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sigil-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aemon_Rivers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Aemon's mother is a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Charlton\" title=\"House Charlton\">House Charlton</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sigil_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sigil-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> He has a daughter named <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Rivers_(daughter_of_Aemon)\" title=\"Walda Rivers (daughter of Aemon)\">Walda</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> It is currently unknown if Aemon is married and thus Walda is a legitimate child, or if she is a bastard.\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />woman</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dashed black\"><div style=